{
  "stem": "25423.6",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a Ukrainian born in the United States, and he asked me silly question about the uniforms of the Ukrainian police, their weapons, what was their authority.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He obviously was not very familiar with the subject and the whole cross-examination, which was designed to point out, to destroy my credibility, was-- just back-fired.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not while I was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He has not reported that he was serving in the Ukrainian police, and that he was a commanding officer of the Ukrainian police in Rawa Ruska.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He has-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did not disclose it when-- in the usual questionnaire.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he obtained American citizenship illegally.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And consequently, as a war criminal, he was stripped of it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was, eventually, a verdict, after other testimonies were taken.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I wasn't interested.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And eventually the court decided that he has violated the laws of the United States and will be stripped, according to the-- to the legislation, which is-- was introduced by Elizabeth Holtzman, and some other legislation on the subject of his citizenship.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He appealed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the appeal, I think, went up to the Supreme Court and was rejected.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he died before being deported.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were some threats on my life, as well as threats on the judge's life.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I have no idea, and this was reported to me by the FBI.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, but most of them are dead.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Most of them died over the years and today, I'm probably one or two survivors of the old group which existed when I was with them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I have very friendly relationship with the order, which still exists in Poland.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They know of me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my brother and I, within our means, make a contribution.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They are rebuilding their monasteries.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
